Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.87,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\frz21.1\c&HD2BEB4&\pos(1064.667,443.334)}给旭姬打了电话。\N但她不接。
